	<item key="ids_opac_cardProtocol" value="Card Protocol" />
	<item key="ids_opac_protocolParagraph1" value="To establish the good cooperative relationship between the bank and the enterprise, and to improve the mutual development and the long term cooperation of both parties."/>
	<item key="ids_opac_protocolParagraph2" value="I.	Party B is willing to take Party A as an important primary client, and put Party A in a preferential position when providing various credit fund supports and other high-quality financial services, under the premise of keeping in compliance with laws and financial policies." />
	<item key="ids_opac_protocolParagraph3" value="II.	Party B will provide Party A with all-round credit services including the working capital loans, capital construction loans, technological transformation loans, reserve loans, real estate loans, and bill acceptance and discount according to the conditions and process for loans." />
	<item key="ids_opac_protocolParagraph4" value="III.	Party B will try its best to satisfy Party A's reasonable demand for working capital loans. Party A shall maintain a good financial structure, in which the current ratio shall be controlled as above____%, the account receivable turnover ratio above____%, and the asset-liability ratio below____%." />
	<item key="ids_opac_protocolParagraph5" value="IV.	Party B will actively support Party A in its capital construction and technological transformation. For Party A’s projects which have been listed in the programs by the authorities, Party B will give assessment as soon as possible; and for the committed projects, Party B shall make a preferential arrangement in its annual credit program and ensure the timely fund supply." />
